data.title: Peter Collins 1953 statistics
data.meta_description: Discover Peter Collins's 1953 Formula 1 World Championship stats, including detailed performance progression throughout the season.
data.text: In the 1953 Formula 1 season Peter Collins drove a total of 4 races for HWM. From the total of 4 races, Peter managed to finish on a 8th place during the 1953 Dutch Grand Prix. If we take a look at the races, where Collins didn't finish, this happend in 2 occasions. The best result for Peter during qualifying was at the 1953 Dutch Grand Prix as 16th fastest.
